\deftab720 {\pard\nisusnos\ltrpar\pardirnatural\ql {\f1 Rick Sowash\rquote s Compositions for Cello:\par
\par
Simply by asking, any cellist can receive free PDFs of the full score-and-parts for any or all of my cello works as well as links to mp3 recordings.   \par
\par
Email me at:  }}{\field {\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "mailto:rick@sowash.com"}{\fldrslt {\cs107\f1\ul\ulc1\cf1 rick@sowash.com}}}{\pard\nisusnos\ltrpar\pardirnatural\ql {\f1 .\par
\par
It\rquote s my policy to give away my music to anyone who is interested in discovering it.  No permission is required to print the PDFs or perform the music.  \par
\par
My musical ideas came to me for free; I simply pass them along.\par
\par
